sequenceDiagram
    participant Cap as CaptureService
    participant Vis as VisionService
    participant Tim as TimingEngine
    participant Inp as InputService
    participant UI as UI/Overlay
    Cap->>Vis: Frame + timestamp
    Vis->>Vis: ROI裁剪 + HSV金色mask
    Vis->>Vis: 圆/外圈/长条/尾端检测
    Vis->>Tim: KeySignal(key, score, predicted_ms_to_hit)
    Tim->>Inp: KeyDown / KeyUp / Tap
    Tim->>UI: 状态、分数、事件
